<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.5.1">
<l>tūmpuṭaip paṉaikkai vēḻan tuyarkeṭut taruḷi maṉṉu</l>
<l>kāmpuṭaik kuṉṟa mēntik kaṭumaḻai kātta ventai</l>
<l>pūmpuṉal poṉṉi muṟṟum pukuntupoṉ varaṉṟa veṅkum</l>
<l>tēmpoḻil kamaḻum nāṅkūrt tirumaṇik kūṭat tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our father who, having granted grace by destroying the sorrows</l>
<l rend="indent">of the elephant with a large, hollow trunk,</l>
<l>Protected against the harsh rain, bearing a hill with sturdy bamboo,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirumaṇikkūṭam in Nāṅkūr where honeyed groves</l>
<l rend="indent">scent [the air] everywhere,</l>
<l>As the wide waters of the Poṉṉi, at its full reach, pile up gold.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
